{
  "stem": "8569.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] We weren't aware-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] of the war, of course, until there was mobilization in 1939 already.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The focus, as far as I was concerned, was really on the Polish invincibility.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had at that time at the head of the Polish government a Marshall Smigly-Rydz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were all kinds of songs linked with his name, that as long as he's the leader of Poland, nothing is going to happen to Poland and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was more in that sense that we were aware.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If there were any changes?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not from the Jewish point of view, I don't think.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What about anti-Semitic incidents?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I was aware as a child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I am aware now, but I wasn't then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as you know from history, Poland was the only country that stood against Nazis for about two, three weeks, I believe.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And during that time, we were in Warsaw, and Warsaw was quite destroyed by the bombing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very frightening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to go to the makeshift bomb shelters, which were in the cellars under the buildings.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ordinarily, those cellars would contain potatoes and coal for the winter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were huge.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They weren't clean, so we used to go there when the alerts-- the sirens of the impending bombing used to come.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We used to run to those shelters, and were always covered with dust of coal, because it was there still from the coal.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "On the one hand, this was my opportunity for the first time to meet our neighbors.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On the other hand, we were sitting there, and we used to listen to the airplanes going by.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were always experts, and they knew, those are ours, those are theirs.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
